## ðŸ“Œ Overview

This ethical judgment framework simulates human-like ethical decision-making  
by implementing a **4-layer ego-based processing model** and a **recursive moral feedback loop.**  
It integrates emotion reception, reflective delay, alignment with internal values, and refined response.

